{"tid":182792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麥花臣球賽爆毆鬥 警犬進場制止","createTime":"2017-04-01T14:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T14:57:00.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ae8c399726a6175473c34b97a30b55b93e67b39","tid":182792,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T14:57:00.000Z","msg":"踢波踢出火！旺角麥花臣球場，晚上7時許有2隊業餘足球隊對賽，據報雙方鬥至2比2，有人對賽果不滿，球員之間發生毆鬥，場面一度失控。警方接報場，派出警犬到場制止打鬥，事後有2名非洲裔球員報稱受傷，警方正追查3名涉案中國男子的下落，案件暫列打交跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170401/large/1491053817_b89c.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170401%2Flarge%2F1491053817_b89c.jpg&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcytr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=161ff82c\" target=\"_blank\">http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170401/large/1491053817_b89c.jpg</a>"}]}